    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM2.10.6">
<l>uṟiyārnta naṟuveṇṇe yoḷiyāl ceṉṟaṅ kuṇṭāṉaik kaṇṭāycci yuralō ṭārkka</l>
<l>taṟiyārnta karuṅkaḷiṟē pōla niṉṟu taṭaṅkaṇkaḷ paṉimalkun taṉmai yāṉai</l>
<l>veṟiyārnta malarmakaḷnā maṅkai yōṭu viyaṉkalaiyeṇ tōḷiṉāḷ viḷaṅku celvac</l>
<l>ceṟiyārnta maṇimāṭan tikaḻntu tōṉṟun tirukkōva lūrataṉuḷ kaṇṭēṉ nāṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The one whose appearance was with wide eyes filled with tears,</l>
<l rend="indent">standing like a dark elephant tied to a stake,</l>
<l rend="indent">when the herdess tied [him] to a mortar,</l>
<l>Having seen him who ate the fragrant ghee which filled the [storage] nets</l>
<l rend="indent">going there by stealth,</l>
<l>I saw in Tirukkōvalūr where mansions appear shining</l>
<l rend="indent">with densely spread jewels,</l>
<l>[Having] the renowned wealth of the lady of the fragrance-filled blossom,</l>
<l rend="indent">[along] with the lady of speech, and the eight-armed one</l>
<l rend="indent">on the wonderous stag.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
